        ]
      },
      "date": "2012-12-20 14:51:09.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on el6/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/718bccd0-4ab4-11e2-b87e-52540035b04c).  Ran 2 tests.  1 tests failed: lustre-initialization-1.",
