      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "09a1dcd067eca2924a332a66ee72121c2459477a",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 117,
        "name": "Andreas Dilger",
        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2012-12-21 10:01:41.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nLooks like this died during OST mount in:\n\n llog_lvfs_write_blob+0x2cd/0x460\n llog_lvfs_write_rec\n llog_write_rec\n llog_write\n mgc_copy_handler\n llog_process_thread\n keys_fill\n llog_process_thread_daemonize\n\ndue to the removal of fsfilt_ext3_write_rec().  I'm surprised that there are still users of fsfilt after the landing of orion onto master?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "77d0f9d5388dbdf2c335a242e78a87d7a9e320f2",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 118,
        "name": "Mikhail Pershin",
        "email": "mpershin@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "tappro"
      },
      "date": "2012-12-21 14:15:48.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nYes, this is 'local copy' of logs on mgc side which exists in master but not in orion. We need just ticket to convert that too to  OSD API",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "809bde42f29e247e317b095c280828eb4bca2eb8",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 117,
        "name": "Andreas Dilger",
        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2013-01-12 06:36:27.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nWhile I'd be happier to see all of fsfilt.c be deleted, perhaps this patch could be refreshed to leave the few in-use functions (fsfilt_get_ops(), fsfilt_setup(), fsfilt_get_label() though this could be removed easily, fsfilt_put_ops(), fsfilt_read_record(), fsfilt_write_record(), fsfilt_start_log(), fsfilt_commit()) in place and delete the rest?\n\nThat would at least allow this patch series to move forward, and still get rid of a lot of cruft.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
