      "message": "Patch Set 4: Looks good to me, approved\n\nChris, from my previous code review it at least appears like you have left the remaining in-use fsfilt functions in place.  I believe that Mike is working to remove the remaining fsfilt callers needed for making local config log copies.\n\nIt would also be possible to have follow-up patch move over the map_inode_pages() code to osd-ldiskfs in advance of removing the remaining fsfilt code.",
